## 🧠 Supported Design Patterns

- ✅ Multi-step Workflow
- ✅ Agent with Contextual Actions
- ✅ RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation)
- ✅ Map Reduce
- ✅ Structured YAML Output

> See [docs/guide.md](./docs/guide.md) for examples and best practices.

