## 📁 Project Structure

```
kernelmind/
├── core.py          # Core logic: Point + Line
├── utils/           # External API wrappers (LLM, search, etc.)
├── examples/        # Use cases (Agent, RAG, Workflow)
├── tests/           # Unit tests
├── docs/guide.md    # Developer documentation
```

